BROWN
v.
KROGER CO., et al. No. 257A05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 18, 2005. Faith Herndon, for Vonda Kay Brown.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 18th day of July 2005 by Defendants to Strike:

"Motion Dismissed as moot by order of the Court in conference this the 18th day of August 2005."
